                <general translate="label comment">
                    <label>General</label>
                    <comment><![CDATA[
<div class="box"> 
<p class="grand-total"><b>Cart2Quote (c2q_v1600-v1702_v2.4.1) provided by <a href="http://www.ophirah.nl">Ophirah | e-commerce projects</a></b></p>
For documentation and support visit <a href="http://cart2quote.zendesk.com">cart2quote.zendesk.com</a>  or contact: <a href="mailto:support@cart2quote.com">support@cart2quote.com</a>
</div>
